795
01:52:39,825 --> 01:52:42,191
Apakah pengungsi minat anda selanjutnya?

796
01:52:42,394 --> 01:52:44,828
Apakah anda akan meliput manusia perahu?

797
01:52:45,030 --> 01:52:46,156
Tidak.

798
01:52:46,365 --> 01:52:48,061
Kau mau teh?

799
01:52:49,034 --> 01:52:52,629
